Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: An investment opportunity in the trendy neighborhood of Old Strathcona. Easy access for pedestrians and vehicles off Saskatchewan drive. Located in one of Edmonton's most densely populated residential areas. In close proximity to U of A. Good onsite parking for customers. Consists of three units: Fumaca  Brazilian Steakhouse 3,550 sq. ft, AM PM Convenience Store 2,340 sq. ft. and Dry Cleaners 2,000 sq. ft.  With 211 Residential Units above.
